    <h4>Biography</h4>
    <div class='note'>
      <p>I work for Texas Instruments Inc, Bangalore since 2004.</p>
<p>Worked extensively on Power Management on Nuclues &amp; Symbian OS, presently on Linux.</p>
<p>Also worked in areas of connectivity(<span class="caps">USB</span>) and <span class="caps">SIM</span> drivers.</p>
